<p></p>



<p>Except in perception that android body is not remote, but surrounding, like a body glove suspended in a control room which is located inside the head of the giant android body that it controls.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-77.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="400" height="323" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Wwon_R-cgpEj7RoqYM11qKHRpldURiRut9uAxVpeI6E=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03Ny5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTQwMCUyQzMyMyZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/srmO3mhn9V5Deo2yuPmyUnama9PPm-F4dGQ0rNX9-Gs=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03Ny5wbmc_dz00MDAmc3NsPTE= 400w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/MolTVrRFlcZ_UzvfYxZUYRm0fCAeF7dS-4HZ0CmwGvA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03Ny5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI0MiZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>And projected into that control room is a volumetric colored replica of the surrounding environment constructed on the basis of sensory input.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-78.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="400" height="324" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/NSqfKn1etVYmXiiCsaLHL9XEfsWTu6zePXqdEPqCe0Y=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03OC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTQwMCUyQzMyNCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/izIghNj2aVti1fZRBNBjVjuH3rCo2fbpOx1rS_cHquA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03OC5wbmc_dz00MDAmc3NsPTE= 400w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/D8c18-sOW28aPXA75VN3kJMh9z3Y6dsUPYJyHZfk14E=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03OC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI0MyZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>As the controller cavorts about in this synthetic reality, the larger android body cavorts in the external world, giving the controller the impression that he is interacting with the external world directly…</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-79.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="450" height="367" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/_K7C4Y3IuvNr9zsdGXOMGGCUaHzbMcXvtzPUY0iAwb4=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03OS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTQ1MCUyQzM2NyZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/QrHlO2YCtO1ynKOB315QAsGaTjUe6Oh9is_nsCSgAHM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03OS5wbmc_dz00NTAmc3NsPTE= 450w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Zct3rv7c04mM8KLn6mNiCiJC1eVDYVkMD27mr4ODfJ8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS03OS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI0NSZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>…although there are also times when it becomes abundantly clear that our view of the world is not direct or unmediated.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-80.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="298" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/j2S4-WzBzeWkwGSpfTj-mrmkKrlvu-ZOQhk3pxsGI-Y=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI5OCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/7DV-ay2yKAnvYdvOdNmKuKODPxbor09el6BebxBYoTo=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MC5wbmc_dz0zMDAmc3NsPTE= 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/JaIj-5-aoAIVM4HONEdLBP3duYW_6D66BVCLxuo_1qU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTE1MCUyQzE1MCZzc2w9MQ== 150w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/77RswqEnyRqD7dmSC_JaTc1wQx6yTYlnWeYxiOqY6rI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTIwMCUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ== 200w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/_RjdAeC26Geai1mEVzhmurFa3yBMuFqOPT3FFhYBUGU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>Now despite appearances to the contrary, the little man at the center of our world of experience is not the viewer or ‘experiencer’ of the surrounding virtual world. The body-image homunculus is just the interface between perceptual and motor function, expressed as an explicit model of the body in an explicit model of surrounding space.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-81.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="400" height="133" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/s-laRl53uMclNkaTUmCKFmdQQGAKnZo7zDm7UkwF09c=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTQwMCUyQzEzMyZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/-1OvApooUtvVo-lktFcLOcQmSZh7TIJ4xYxWJm0vvxk=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MS5wbmc_dz00MDAmc3NsPTE= 400w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/96Eec8JL91sxdkMw1VtSeZmeOcuSpG_Rg9kB6UZIqak=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04MS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzEwMCZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>Motor computation takes the form of spatial field-like forces in that space, that bend the body-image homunculus into different postures…</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-82.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="400" height="152" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/ngmMUxPRj6nTVnyifzJVc1lU1bCsZOSJASrUZVsMve8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Mi5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTQwMCUyQzE1MiZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/PBLuSZetAFpQiFh43cQZ-4Pe0VVogZrPMLuDQ5E_FbU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Mi5wbmc_dz00MDAmc3NsPTE= 400w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/UUdLC_2yllLFb7eZNw32_90IIQILVrIcuKh-Q2iRe48=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Mi5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzExNCZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>…and those postures are then mirrored in amplified form by the larger android body.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-83.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="200" height="202" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/q8BhhAnuoRr0RvipDrJCQWd4IW6ifLxTl5ThOHOTcfU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04My5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTIwMCUyQzIwMiZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/UISrJn-xcDbNA09wnb-qTAUGIUgML2dPW-2Nha7pdoI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04My5wbmc_dz0yMDAmc3NsPTE= 200w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/DkfkOYJMFgJem3gbKN6FPXv06EQEXI1bsSt5LQUArTc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04My5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>But the coupling works both ways. Forces from the external world are also communicated back in to the model world. For example gravity drags the android body downwards against the ground that pushes upward…</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-84.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="291" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/zib3jhiZPqxTcWlyNpJFA-TRanB23ly3X5hPWPa4xhM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04NC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI5MSZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/FLXvrYADqvA1mcaVBiwAW5QMGVk_6sEeJOMLqi6uYfE=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04NC5wbmc_dz0zMDAmc3NsPTE= 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/mCLmQDnoAGGZz_7ADAWaZfEUHspwZxbUPTMTWO-RQ3I=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04NC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>…and these forces are also replicated in the model environment where we perceive them as actual forces in what we believe to be the external world. The perceived force of synthetic gravity makes sense of the persistent resistance felt to upward motion of the body, just as the resistance of the ground underfoot to penetration is perceived as an upward force of rigid support.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-85.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="291" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/p04YsnCwcN9ATSIXz3tY4J5ViMe8ifn7zXrU0IrLgXM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04NS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI5MSZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/CTz9J1t4Qsp0FEjGj24t8thGvliRxg4kwf80tx0ROiE=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04NS5wbmc_dz0zMDAmc3NsPTE= 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/lWp0BFk8BLDuBTJKlwWqtubovQx31nJQJn15Qyf9J0g=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04NS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>We resist forces like the pull of gravity by constructing an equal and opposite force of <em>levity</em>, that raises our body-image homunculus upward against the downward pull while pushing downward against the ground. This symmetrically opposed motor force field is a spatial thought that appears under voluntary control, and it acts on the body image as a motor command. And as the motor force field moves the body-image homunculus…</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-86.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="130" height="300" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Xs31Lg8ZQBz7nc5iKRmH2ZDt53YEeQMK3f9vsHGpnKI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Ni5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTEzMCUyQzMwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>…the larger android body moves in perfect synchrony with it, pushing harder against the ground to raise itself upward against gravity.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-87.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="628" height="300" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/oOcZLEVQ9-edTnkBVNWFvlcsWREpu3nwXUyVzAv8Acc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Ny5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTYyOCUyQzMwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/idRxihsDOaRsC6P8JnaDsprlYkOjtaEoW6_eSYRSJx0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Ny5wbmc_dz02Mjgmc3NsPTE= 628w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/tNGGjkGDCrSD_hlMaRHJ2Wa2uK1ld7tuqo7vxBF6AlY=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04Ny5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzE0MyZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>We move our hand by simply willing it to move in any direction we choose, and that will is itself a force that acts on our body-image hand which moves in response to the willed force. The larger android hand moves in synchrony, as if it were itself under the influence of a larger external force pulling it in the willed direction.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-88.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="295" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/9B-xXDyeOoukKC0l_S3ihwDdKSBjEBGd_CieVfsPtN8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04OC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI5NSZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/LB_K2-nYftEkF_p6kgNuNm6JEHpGRj_YjuwKEOxXF7g=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04OC5wbmc_dz0zMDAmc3NsPTE= 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/eoUhxbQpn0jxyW_lGiD2mWVH6etDaA_dw5E15QB4otA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04OC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>And our desire to move through the world is expressed as a larger force field that pulls on the entire body-image homunculus. But since the homunculus is anchored to the center of the control room, the only way he can advance forward…</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-89.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="295" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/uceEHo5GbYIMa55Tr7UNaKsbDq-N6IO9XJCtjV6-_FY=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04OS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI5NSZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/j2HSsWH-hFF3or-1i6Zf10R8BD8ag67l85N5lWNdaZM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04OS5wbmc_dz0zMDAmc3NsPTE= 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/9YPs46RPIvBJfkV6tHMuUb0XgnuKxhm4811YKoNL_Qo=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS04OS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>…is by pushing the world backwards until his destination comes to where he is, or so it seems perceptually, resulting in real progress of the physical body through the physical world.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-90.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="252" height="225" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/XaRPEsTVtDx6QyCp0hb3IMW3QFWhFBaYDOfUi1J3jTI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05MC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTI1MiUyQzIyNSZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>Perceived objects in the perceived environment also exert attractive and aversive forces that influence the movement of our body through the world. So whenever we perceive an object to be attractive, it automatically exudes an attractive field that tends to pull our body image towards it in perceptual space.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-91.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="246" height="225" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/sV-DvAHEVl4qfCzRkrphHWclG3-FahjhnBvNsS6lt-A=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05MS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTI0NiUyQzIyNSZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>The larger body moves through external space exactly as if it were responding directly to field forces from the external world, except that these forces actually exist only in the internal perceptual world.</p>



<p><a href="http://slehar.com/wwwRel//cartoonepist/cartoonepist53.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><strong>(Follow alternate argument path <em>backwards</em>)</strong></a></p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-92.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="305" height="256" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/tci5PRyhHKsoaApJF5cKf5lRCJXfZeWNdBaNmam3qY4=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Mi5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwNSUyQzI1NiZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/nMl7upsnx71T_y5UvaMsmDBMy4PLEMm3O2K4qjoTrhE=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Mi5wbmc_dz0zMDUmc3NsPTE= 305w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/-ubkO5fcERMEm7StvQQVxgV8Ai78av483hppyAtoi6Y=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Mi5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzI1MiZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 305px) 100vw, 305px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>And when we perceive something to be aversive, it automatically exudes a repulsive field that pushes our body away from it in perceptual space.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-93.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="181" height="200" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/jlMIvEsh82EmXO_L5Uw5udMVlKHdnFhiz_aUcXhXR9A=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05My5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTE4MSUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>The subjective impression of being attracted or repelled by attractive and repulsive stimuli is not only metaphorically true, but this subjective impression is a veridical manifestation of the mental mechanism that drives our motor response.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-94.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="203" height="200" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/hp-UfmJqjdw_MdhTsbJXKtQW5r3dTOuTOLU1Yn2CGuI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05NC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTIwMyUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/aQbKVC58VidlQZR-2owpjqN5_ak12qXLJ6CpWkNjEx0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05NC5wbmc_dz0yMDMmc3NsPTE= 203w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/cPoSfQj7J_ug5roKBqYOF2ZnVWRl1ZpUomUPsExgi-A=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05NC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwJTJDNTAmc3NsPTE= 50w" sizes="(max-width: 203px) 100vw, 203px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>So in a sense it <em>is</em> the sensorimotor homunculus for whom the internal world of perception is constructed. But that homunculus does not “see” the internal scene…</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-95.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="200" height="188" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/t7eHXFBM48II39p-8j0rCFYcYRw0pkvRoNHd1aYhZGI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05NS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTIwMCUyQzE4OCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>…but rather the attractive and aversive features recognized in the scene exert forces on the body image homunculus, which in turn result in body motion through the environment.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-96.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="232" height="200" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/2Ahljr1zZDkYFokpLCrfHh8E1YWhOJNQcB2pt8iW1zQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Ni5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTIzMiUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>Once we recognize the world of experience for the internal representation that it is, the computational strategy used in motor control becomes clearly evident by inspection.</p>



<p><em>So you are saying that vision, proprioception, somatosensory, and motor function are all part of a single integrated analog control system? But brain scientists have discovered a fragmented architecture in the cortex with separate areas specialized for processing visual, auditory, and motor information. How would the activations in all those separate cortical areas integrate to produce a single unified experience? What is the binding force that binds them all together?</em></p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-97.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="351" height="200" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/LLsj6O61Y5yt1Yx_PyKxtQm1Gp6IDRQl_HUFPGTPM0w=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Ny5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTM1MSUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/CQrvhzke67JXpd9c7bgxUcL-v8S1miHPQ4l6ErmmGRQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Ny5wbmc_dz0zNTEmc3NsPTE= 351w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/sbEEB0pNSp5FyedAMABQ1IE__LMazepI4a2Lhhbo_A0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05Ny5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzE3MSZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 351px) 100vw, 351px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>They are bound together by bi-directional causal connections, just like the dual controls of an airplane. If the student pulls the stick back while the instructor is pushing it forward, both control sticks move in perfect synchrony because they are connected, exactly as if the two pilots were actually pulling and pushing on the same stick.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-98.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="542" height="200" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/5x1kXeXvEMBpyBjt_UDdmp369PFQDhlPNEP1eUW5klM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05OC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTU0MiUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/EjTZc_L49VfHSHjRXNLexHLdw-TC0HiWuhhFFIjRjgY=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05OC5wbmc_dz01NDImc3NsPTE= 542w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/MvOJ3l0UssszQuAOegMfFpyIlqf6n4lELobXMXdgDDM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05OC5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzExMSZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 542px) 100vw, 542px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>In the same way, the different sensory/motor marionettes in different cortical areas are all coupled to each other, as well as to the larger external body, so that forces applied to one marionette are automatically and immediately transmitted in parallel to all the rest.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-99.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="504" height="200" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/CE4oS909PBhWG9n8Zv-Y0gaX5jvoSgNENmgBaS6Ojtc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05OS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTUwNCUyQzIwMCZzc2w9MQ==" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/-0jbBlXr6AhblfFPpyb6blPdsiUFM_xS8BrTbq0BueA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05OS5wbmc_dz01MDQmc3NsPTE= 504w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/uN2VNCeTxbAob7_2MDNT7ZYCeTT1QX_n0DAnmxE37T0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS05OS5wbmc_cmVzaXplPTMwMCUyQzExOSZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 504px) 100vw, 504px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>And if different forces are applied to different marionettes, the resultant body motion is exactly as if all of those forces were acting on a single virtual marionette.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-100.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/mNAx4oKWccx21tvALqn2BGp1vhW6BKAtO1bD0UpcaaA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDAucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT03NTElMkMyMDAmc3NsPTE=" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/DnwMgvfSJ4Zy4FX7523M15y4Xd_4Br2q8wnI9OU-zjg=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDAucG5nP3c9NzUxJnNzbD0x 751w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/2G4hjFFTPOrGt3mxx08OMQMn9OKsGq2PrsMC0bX8eHM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDAucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT0zMDAlMkM4MCZzc2w9MQ== 300w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>So visual data is expressed in the visual representation, body posture is represented in the proprioceptive representation, and motor planning is computed in a global motor planning space. But all are coupled to form a single visual/proprioceptive/motor space, which is the space that we experience.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-101.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="431" height="256" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/1W-lSKlfhLDfVECpsvQW1fWIP2OnDDufczrBxSxr6NA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDEucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT00MzElMkMyNTYmc3NsPTE=" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/84KVbae0aRrMoLkI5aVavnXcMxEUzX5w-rhgHMd6rLY=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDEucG5nP3c9NDMxJnNzbD0x 431w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/W0GmPn9U5ALtLClah7YHSzPlJVFGrXjwuffVJtIQGHc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDEucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT0zMDAlMkMxNzgmc3NsPTE= 300w" sizes="(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p>Each of these diverse representations are expressed in their own specialized slab of cortical tissue, although these areas are tightly coupled so as to form a single integrated computational module.</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-102.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="199" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/4tx174nRU8VPtj24m75wy4mknd2eCjILyvYUdd9RnRc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDIucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT0zMDAlMkMxOTkmc3NsPTE=" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p><em>That is the most incredible hypothesis I have ever heard! Tell me honestly now—do you really <strong>believe</strong> this? Or are you being deliberately provocative for the sake of argument?</em></p>



<p>Look—if you once just accept the fact that this world we see around us is a picture in our head, all the rest of it follows by inspection! Besides, the alternative view, that we can somehow see the world directly, bypassing the sensory machinery in the eye and brain, is just plain <strong><em>magic</em></strong>!</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-103.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="226" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/k5PmkVzMXGdbZDnKebAUrajCUXD1HI1FTSfS4XDilfM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDMucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT0zMDAlMkMyMjYmc3NsPTE=" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/VDjKDRpQ--I91Ipz61M7l02b44Iy8G3dEe1HMpQRS18=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDMucG5nP3c9MzAwJnNzbD0x 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/iqkbua2y8wNnFgbG-LT1xDq6s-2EelVT5gEOzxXLYZM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDMucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT0yMDAlMkMxNTAmc3NsPTE= 200w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p></p>



<p><em>So it comes down to a choice between two incredible hypotheses. Either you believe the incredible notion that your skull is larger than the entire perceived universe…</em></p>



<p>…or you believe the absurd notion that we can experience things outside of ourselves directly, beyond the sensory surface! One of these two incredible hypotheses simply must be true, and the other is just plain wrong!</p>



<figure><a href="https://i0.wp.com/qualiacomputing.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-104.png?ssl=1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img width="300" height="148" src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/mKW7QLKvvQR-IajF47ugOJl09GK_GoPceu7InEV8jco=/aHR0cHM6Ly9pMC53cC5jb20vcXVhbGlhY29tcHV0aW5nLmNvbS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMi8xMi9pbWFnZS0xMDQucG5nP3Jlc2l6ZT0zMDAlMkMxNDgmc3NsPTE=" alt="" loading="lazy"/></a></figure>


<p>Which one do <strong><em>YOU</em></strong> find less incredible?</p>







